room_title: Escape room "Olympus Under Siege" by Elusive Escape Rooms in Wisconsin Dells
review: Tried the Olympus Siege Room, with only my younger sister, and failed. However, it was a blast and the employees were great. Definitely going back!

room_title: Escape room "Olympus Under Siege" by Elusive Escape Rooms in Wisconsin Dells
review: We had a great time last night doing the Olympus Under Siege room. Ian was great to work with! We had so much fun, we decided to come back today to take on the Butcher. Again, a great time! Thea was a lot of fun as our room master! Highly recommended.
